commit.message: Fix warning about maybe uninitialized variable in trivial resampler
Fix building for SDL version < 1.3
Fix audio locking

Simplify sdl_backend API

Audio generated by N64 is always 16-bit stereo. BITRATE is not related
to sample depth at all. So we can simplify set_format and rename it as
set_frequency.
Improve debugging when obtained spec differs from desired spec.
build: Allow out of tree builds.

Revert "Allow non-default compilers without resorting to symbolic links"

This reverts commit 7155ae6f21f88a92050ba812fed6645141234d2e, as it conflicts with GNU make which always defines default values for certain variables
